Cheng Chen was inspired to make the suit after watching the hit film with his brother . 
  He spent six months researching and building the replica to the movie's exact measurements . 
  The finished product is two metres high and weighs just 4kg and comes with helmet, gloves and backpack . 
  Cheng said he was was too 'chubby' to fit into it himself so he asked his nephew to model it . 
 